1. The flexibility of the glass screen protector is the same as the plastic material, is it tempered glass or plastic? This screen protector is a real tempered glass. The plastic flexibility is the exact reason why we call it tempered glass screen protector. Tempered glass is a type of safety glass that is stronger than ordinary glass. 2. It cannot be seen from the appearance that it is glass or plastic. As a customer, what can we do to identify it? There is an easy, quick, cost-effective way to test it yourself, and it's very accurate. Most plastics have a melting point between 160 and 210 degrees Celsius, and glass materials are at least over 1400 degrees Celsius, so is there a lighter around? 3. Does it come with a cleaning wipe to use prior to placing on the phone? Yes, the package includes: 6*Guide Stickers, 3*Wet Wipe & 3*Dry Wipe, 3*Dust Absorber 4. How can I remove bubbles? Use the kit in the package to clean the screen before placing the screen protector. If there are bubbles,try to gently press the bubbles with your finger or with a ruler,but the screen surface needs a thin cloth pad to avoid scratching the protector. 5. How can I remove a cracked glass screen protector? Lift the screen protector with the card from any corner of the screen protector, then hold the corner and remove slowly. (If you find CHIP or CRACK on the screen protector, for your safety, please wear gloves when removing the screen protector.)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to apply!
reviews.reviewText: I like that this comes with 3 screen protectors as well as wet/dry cleaning cloths and stickers to help you property align it on your phone. And the screen protectors are placed individually in a soft packet to keep it clean and scratch free until you are ready to use it. My screen was very dirty (probably from oil from my fave and fingers). I do wish there were additional wet cleaning cloths. Overall a good screen protector at a reasonable price. Definitely recommend and will purchase this again for any family member that’s in need of a new screen protector.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install
reviews.reviewText: I’ve used this brand on several models of iPhone and have been consistently pleased with ease of installation, durability and value. Three to a pack, comes with wet and dry wipes and dust removers. Easy to remove if necessary.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Screen protector fit ok. Tried looking up on website proper installation but web site wasn’t set up to clearly find anything. Seems like it was set up by a fifteen year old. Scanned the QR code like it said and when I arrived at the site there was no real order of things. If it was me I would have set it up starting with newest iPhone then work back then Mac pads etc…etc. couldn’t even find my phone although it just came out last year. No problem though it was easy enough to install. It does look like a quality product and it arrived in a timely manner.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Screen protector too small
reviews.reviewText: Screen protector doesn’t cover enough of the screen. Even though the phone edges are “rounded “ they could have made the screen protector such that it came closer to the edge. No matter what case I put on this phone there is still a gap of exposed screen that will collect dust and debris. I don’t like that.
They sit well. They glide smooth. There are no lifted edges.4/5 stars ONLY because the top speaker cutout collects dust.. otherwise I'd buy more if they were available.
